message.body: Hey Phuong! So I kinda lied. I won't be able to do anything on Thursday cause I have a quiz on Chem Friday and lord knows I need all the help I can get. Can we do Friday? Maybe around like...5 or 6? We can grab dinner and a movie or something.

Hey!!!! Okay seriously, you read my mind! I was going to ask if you wanted to do Friday because I already bookmarked as the day hahah :) so that's awesome! Good luck with your Chem. quiz. You got this since you know, you've been a science rock star and all!
Awesome!!! Now....what movie to watch
Have you seen "Into The Woods" yet???
Nooo!!! Let's do it!
Yes!!!!
Anna Kendrick here we come!
Awesome!!
So Tam and Dominic are going to 20 Manning Grill for Restaurant Week. I told them that we went there for your birthday and to get the noodle steak and chocolate chip cookie for dessert!!!
We should go back!
We totally should!
Seriously, woman, that steak though!
Hahahah!
We could do it for Friday, but it'll either be 515 or 945. Haha. Absurd times.
And it's a prefixed menu so I don't know if they'll be on there.
Oh that's true. I like way your brain and what it does!
*the way
*brain works
Hahah wow
I messed up that sentence!
Haha. We can go anywhere....though. It would be $35 which is pricey for someone with no money. Haha.
I feel ya! Like everything sounds so expensive now!
Probably because I need steady dough.
I agree. Shit is getting serious.
Life
You summed it up sister! Should put that on a banner.
Hahah I'm imagining a "Shit is getting serious. Life." sticker in the back of my car! Pretty much the anthem of life in your 20s.
Haha. I'm gonna see if it's possible to print a sticker and let's just say you'll be getting a little sumthin sumthin for your birfday.
Hahahahahahahahahahah!That would be a fantastic sumthin sumthin :))))
